description: Run an early-stage venture firm from one knowledge base. Five agents source deal flow and score it against your thesis, monitor portfolio health and flag runway risk before it's a crisis, research markets and companies on demand, and publish a daily point of view on your vertical to compound proprietary deal flow. Replaces the scattered stack of CRMs, spreadsheets, and "I'll get to it" follow-ups that every fund secretly runs on.
